  <taxonomy>part.sensor.4.pins</taxonomy>
  <description> &lt;p&gt;MPS20N0040D Sphygmomanometer 0-40kPa Differential Air Pressure Sensor / HX710B ADC Module&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;This module couples a MPS20N0040D sphygmomanometer air pressure sensor module with an HX710B analog-to-digital converter IC. It can be powered from a 3.3V or 5V source, with a claimed measurement range of 0-40kPa. It uses a proprietary 2-wire communication protocol and is thus not I&lt;sup&gt;2&lt;/sup&gt;C compatible.&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;strong&gt;Links: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
	  &lt;li&gt;
		&lt;a href="https://softroboticstoolkit.com/files/sorotoolkit/files/mps20n0040d-s_datasheet.pdf" target="_blank"&gt; MPS20N0040D Datasheet&lt;/a&gt;
	  &lt;/li&gt;
	  &lt;li&gt;
		&lt;a href="https://img.ozdisan.com/ETicaret_Dosya/470782_5454613.PDF" target="_blank"&gt; HX710A/B Datasheet&lt;/a&gt;
	  &lt;/li&gt;
	  &lt;li&gt;
		&lt;a href="https://cdn.sparkfun.com/datasheets/Sensors/ForceFlex/hx711_english.pdf" target="_blank"&gt; HX711 Datasheet&lt;/a&gt;
	  &lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
  </description>
